Ensure you have Python installed on your system.
Install the required libraries by running pip install pygame.
Download the game files and PNG images from the GitHub repository.
Run the game script in your Python environment.
Control the red spaceship using the 'W' and 'S' keys for up and down movement, respectively. Press 'F' to shoot bullets.
Control the yellow spaceship using the arrow keys ('UP' and 'DOWN' keys) for up and down movement, respectively. Press 'L' to shoot bullets.
Avoid getting hit by the opponent's bullets while trying to eliminate their spaceship by shooting your bullets.
The game ends when one player loses all their lives. You will be prompted to restart the game.

